The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Madarsa panel
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Madarsa panel
                            
	Calcutta, April 17: The state cabinet today approved a draft legislation for setting up a Madarsa Service Commission to recruit teachers. The bill will be introduced in the budget session of the Assembly this year.                                                                                                                                                                          
